### Slash Commands with Options

```mrg
slash ban
    description ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏™‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏ä‡∏¥‡∏Å
    option user target ‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ô required
    option string reason ‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏ï‡∏∏‡∏ú‡∏• optional
    ban {target}
    reply ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ô {target} ‡∏™‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏£‡πá‡∏à!
```

### Button Interactions

```mrg
command roles
    button Primary ‡∏ô‡∏±‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ô role_student
    button Success ‡∏≠‡∏≤‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏¢‡πå role_teacher
    send buttons

on button click role_student
    role add ‡∏ô‡∏±‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ô
    reply ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏° role ‡∏ô‡∏±‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß!

on button click role_teacher
    role add ‡∏≠‡∏≤‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏¢‡πå
    reply ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏° role ‡∏≠‡∏≤‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏¢‡πå‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß!
```

### Select Menus

```mrg
command choose
    select menu
        option game ‡πÄ‡∏Å‡∏°
        option music ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏•‡∏á
        option movie ‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏±‡∏á
    send menu

on select menu_choice
    reply ‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å {selected_value}
```

